data.text:
Kane hopes for Bayern 'momentum change' after inspiring CL progress

Bayern Munich secured a comprehensive 3-0 victory over Lazio at Allianz Arena to overturned a 1-0 deficit from the first leg and reach the Champions League last eight.

05/03/24 9:45pm

Kane urges Bayern to keep fighting after Lazio defeat

Bayern Munich striker Harry Kane has called on his side to keep fighting after Ciro Immobile's penalty gave Lazio a 1-0 win in the first leg of their last-16 tie in Rome.

15/02/24 8:30am
